text: Something About Us () is an unaired 2019 romance South Korean television series starring Seo Kang-joon. It is based on the popular webtoon of the same title by Lee Yun-ji which was first published in 2014. ==Synopsis== Han Woo- jin and Do Ga-young have been friends since high school. They began to fall in love after meeting again in university. ==Cast== *Seo Kang-joon as Han Woo-jin ==References== ==External links== * * * Something About Us at Lezhin Comics * Something About Us at Lezhin Comics Category:Korean-language television shows Category:South Korean romance television series Category:Television shows based on South Korean webtoons Category:Unaired television shows
